basic.Peptide Name: SyCPA 123 (chemically synthetic AMPs20; XXD, XXL, fatty acid cyclized lipopeptide, lactam, XXJ, UCSB1e; BBMm)
basic.Source: bioinformatic predicted bacterial nonribosomal gene cluster,Rhodococcus jostiiRHA1, bacteria-derived, natural derivatives
basic.Target Organism: active against B. subtilis 168 1A1 (MIC 4 ug/ml), E. faecium Com15 (MIC 8 ug/ml), S. aureus USA300 (MIC 4 ug/ml), E-coli DH5alpha (MIC>64 ug/ml), K-pneumoniae ATCC 10031 (MIC>64 ug/ml), A. baumannii ATCC 17978 (MIC 8 ug/ml), P-aeruginosa PAO1 (MIC>64 ug/ml), E-cloacae ATCC 14037 (MIC>64 ug/ml), M-tuberculosis H37RV (MIC>12.5 ug/ml).
